    "Our RL method offers advantages over ML methods for determining WCET.",
    "ML-based methods rely on diverse datasets, which are hard to collect [20], and must fit into existing development processes.",
    "In contrast, RL methods adapt based on environmental feedback, reducing the need for extensive labeled data.",
    "Thus, RL provides a more flexible approach for WCET estimation in complex real-time systems.• Inclusion of Diversity in Evaluation Metrics: Another contribution of this thesis is the incorporation of diversity as an essential metric in WCET evaluation.",
    "In the context of GA, diversity is integrated as a separate fitness function, ensuring that a wide range of potential solutions is explored.In RL, diversity influences the calculation of the reward function, promoting exploration over exploitation."
